headers {
  Accept: application/json
}

auth {
  mode: bearer
}

auth:bearer {
  token: {{token}}
}

docs {
  # Keluhin API

  Collection-level Bearer auth: semua request mewarisi `Authorization: Bearer {{token}}`.

  Cara pakai:
  1. Pilih environment **Local** (kanan atas).
  2. Jalankan **Auth / Login** — script post-response otomatis isi var `token`.
  3. Request lain langsung jalan (auth inherit).
}
